{"tid":1931361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世衞澄清沒證據顯示武漢新型冠狀病毒人傳人","createTime":"2020-03-18T06:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T14:00:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":491,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"d02a113788644b95697c37a5b20ef7597a1eea72","tid":1931361,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=376783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376783&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=d97cfb8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D376783&h=ad54beff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=376783</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2020年1月15日 01:18</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】路透社一度引述世界衞生組織指，武漢新型冠狀病毒可能出現有限度人傳人，世衛發言人澄清指，目前未有證據顯示新型病毒出現有限度人傳人。<br />\n<br />\n路透社的報道，起初引述世衞指，武漢新型冠狀病毒出現有限度人傳人，其後報道修改為新型冠狀病毒「可能」在家庭內出現有限度人傳人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>本台發電郵向世衞查詢，世衞發言人澄清指，根據當局初步調查，無明確證據顯示新型冠狀病毒有人傳人，亦沒證據指病毒有限度人傳人。</strong><br />\n<br />\n世衞發言人指，現時未確定病毒的傳播方式，但當患者出現呼吸道感染徵狀，人傳人一直都是關注，需要作進一步研究。<br />\n<br />\n對於密切接觸者或同時間聚集在同一地點的人，很難去確定他們是因為暴露在共同的感染源頭而患病，抑或由一個人將病毒傳給他人，所以要進行流行病學調查和詳細分析。<br />\n<br />\n而武漢衞健委公布，在武漢追踪的763名密切接觸者，有187人已解除醫學觀察，在密切接觸者當中沒發現相關病例。<br />\n<br />\n另外，正在泰國隔離治療的女患者，與她密切接觸的人士已經回國，並正接受醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前Wuhuan Hygiene Office咁樣講"},{"pid":"9b561681ba2a042495ac822abe7abb7da96f7284","tid":1931361,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":274,"score":-272,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"標題黨定舊聞?"},{"pid":"4c6780310e4ffc4f0a2ecc39f2aff98903e56847","tid":1931361,"uid":51271,"like":283,"dislike":1,"score":282,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2020年1月15日 01:18</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當香港人聞到有伏味果時，Wuhuan Hygiene Office仲話沒事兒沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"b4ce51b0c6cf860fd5a9386ffb4215e9a760035c","tid":1931361,"uid":174013,"like":348,"dislike":2,"score":346,"quote":{"pid":"9b561681ba2a042495ac822abe7abb7da96f7284","tid":1931361,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":274,"score":-272,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"標題黨定舊聞?"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"你文盲定弱智？"},{"pid":"a4d028763ab8329e05490b3a43a847a053f9555b","tid":1931361,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ce51b0c6cf860fd5a9386ffb4215e9a760035c","tid":1931361,"uid":174013,"like":348,"dislike":2,"score":346,"quote":{"pid":"9b561681ba2a042495ac822abe7abb7da96f7284","tid":1931361,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":274,"score":-272,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"標題黨定舊聞?"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"你文盲定弱智？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fec3d77be2c104e49ca740c7c07d22ded9dafe1","tid":1931361,"uid":2772,"like":125,"dislike":1,"score":124,"quote":{"pid":"b4ce51b0c6cf860fd5a9386ffb4215e9a760035c","tid":1931361,"uid":174013,"like":348,"dislike":2,"score":346,"quote":{"pid":"9b561681ba2a042495ac822abe7abb7da96f7284","tid":1931361,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":274,"score":-272,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"標題黨定舊聞?"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"你文盲定弱智？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"冇證據顯示佢唔係弱智"},{"pid":"97a2f4cb4f5133dbb7e6b85d3769c0d4037462e7","tid":1931361,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"得閒拎出嚟鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47d79b7af3a4fa7c392e918e759051d3e5e1989","tid":1931361,"uid":184756,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"十分喜愛鞭屍post"},{"pid":"bd3b072e51d4ae